  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The primary aim of this french multicenter national study is to assess and compare time to
      quality of life score deterioration (targeted dimensions : global health, fatigue and
      emotional functionning of EORTC QLQC30 according to the first line chemotherapy associated
      with bevacizumab in metastatic colorectal patients.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
